240
00:19:39,428 --> 00:19:42,218
KEMBANG API

241
00:19:45,517 --> 00:19:46,887
Bayi Setan.

242
00:19:48,061 --> 00:19:49,521
Pernah menyalakan ini?

243
00:19:49,605 --> 00:19:51,225
Tidak. Apa keren?

244
00:19:51,690 --> 00:19:54,190
- Kau meremehkan.
- Tak seperti mangkuk.

245
00:19:54,776 --> 00:19:56,316
Ini jauh lebih bagus.

246
00:19:56,570 --> 00:19:59,320
Ada alasannya tertulis "18 tahun ke atas".

247
00:19:59,698 --> 00:20:04,198
Ini isinya 150 butir bubuk hitam.

248
00:20:04,453 --> 00:20:06,123
Alias bubuk mesiu.

249
00:20:07,122 --> 00:20:10,132
Ikat dua, maka akan lebih besar
dari M-80.

250
00:20:10,500 --> 00:20:11,460
Ikat lima,

251
00:20:12,294 --> 00:20:14,674
kita akan punya dinamit.

252
00:20:14,755 --> 00:20:17,165
Kau mau membunuhnya
dengan kembang api?

253
00:20:17,257 --> 00:20:18,627
Ada ide lebih baik?

254
00:20:19,051 --> 00:20:20,221
Ya. Eleven.

255
00:20:21,553 --> 00:20:24,353
Melawan makhluk itu?
Dia akan butuh bantuan.

256
00:20:25,390 --> 00:20:26,640
Astaga.

257
00:20:27,184 --> 00:20:28,194
Pegang ini.

258
00:20:32,731 --> 00:20:33,821
Sakit?

259
00:20:34,983 --> 00:20:36,113
Lumayan.

260
00:20:37,194 --> 00:20:38,994
Kau akan punya bekas luka.

261
00:20:39,488 --> 00:20:41,158
Akan tampak lebih jagoan.

262
00:20:41,240 --> 00:20:42,120
Keren.

263
00:20:42,199 --> 00:20:43,869
Ya, keren.

264
00:20:47,204 --> 00:20:48,084
El...

265
00:20:49,039 --> 00:20:49,919
Ya?

266
00:20:50,207 --> 00:20:51,917
Aku mau beri tahu sesuatu.

267
00:20:52,334 --> 00:20:55,004
Hanya saja, putus,

268
00:20:55,087 --> 00:20:56,257
itu sulit.

269
00:20:59,591 --> 00:21:03,141
Aku suka kau dan Max berteman.

270
00:21:03,720 --> 00:21:07,310
Hanya saja aku cemburu, awalnya,
dan marah.

271
00:21:07,391 --> 00:21:09,481
Itu sebabnya aku berkata bodoh.

272
00:21:09,559 --> 00:21:11,649
Dan ingin kau milikku saja.

273
00:21:12,813 --> 00:21:14,563
Kini aku sadar itu tak adil.

274
00:21:14,648 --> 00:21:17,438
Dan egois. Dan... maafkan aku.

275
00:21:18,860 --> 00:21:22,450
Aku belum pernah seperti ini,
dengan siapa pun...

276
00:21:23,156 --> 00:21:24,196
dan...

277
00:21:26,326 --> 00:21:28,536
Konon itu membuatmu gila.

278
00:21:29,288 --> 00:21:31,038
Apa yang membuatmu gila?

279
00:21:32,582 --> 00:21:34,422
Kau belum dengar istilah itu...

280
00:21:34,668 --> 00:21:36,498
Kau tahu, ungkapan itu...

281
00:21:36,753 --> 00:21:38,673
"membuatmu gila", seperti...

282
00:21:39,798 --> 00:21:42,008
- "Teman wanita"?
- Bukan.

283
00:21:42,092 --> 00:21:44,392
- "Teman pria."
- Bukan juga.

284
00:21:44,469 --> 00:21:46,809
- Seperti perasaan atau...
- Perasaan...

285
00:21:46,888 --> 00:21:50,098
Ya, seperti... Orang tua
kadang saling mengatakannya.

286
00:21:50,183 --> 00:21:51,183
- Orang tua?
- Ya.

287
00:21:51,268 --> 00:21:54,018
Yang ingin kubilang

288
00:21:54,271 --> 00:21:55,611
bahwa aku...

289
00:21:55,689 --> 00:21:57,769
Aku tahu aku...

290
00:21:59,359 --> 00:22:02,609
Kuulangi... ini kode merah.

291
00:22:03,989 --> 00:22:05,319
- Dustin?
- Mike?

292
00:22:05,699 --> 00:22:07,409
- Dustin!
- Mike!

293
00:22:07,492 --> 00:22:10,002
Kau harus dengar. Aku memang menghilang,

294
00:22:10,078 --> 00:22:13,168
dan maaf, bukan karena marah.
Maksudku, memang,

295
00:22:13,248 --> 00:22:15,668
tapi juga karena terjebak di bawah tanah

296
00:22:15,751 --> 00:22:16,921
di markas rahasia Rusia.

297
00:22:18,670 --> 00:22:21,510
Dustin, kau terlalu cepat. Aku tak paham.

298
00:22:21,590 --> 00:22:24,760
Memang terdengar gila,
tapi orang Rusia sudah masuk ke Hawkins.

299
00:22:24,843 --> 00:22:26,053
Orang Rusia!

300
00:22:26,136 --> 00:22:28,306
Kini... mereka gunakan... membuka gerbang.

301
00:22:28,472 --> 00:22:29,852
Dustin, terputus-putus.

302
00:22:29,931 --> 00:22:32,181
Kini kami dikejar,
dan tak ada jalan keluar,

303
00:22:32,267 --> 00:22:34,307
aku ingin kau menjemput.
Nancy bisa menyetir?

304
00:22:34,394 --> 00:22:35,354
Kami akan...

305
00:22:36,188 --> 00:22:37,608
Dustin, kau terputus.

306
00:22:37,981 --> 00:22:39,941
- Mike?
- Dustin, kau di sana?

307
00:22:40,025 --> 00:22:41,435
Mike, kau di sana?

308
00:22:41,693 --> 00:22:42,653
Dustin...

309
00:22:44,196 --> 00:22:46,816
Jangan sekarang. Kumohon. Mike!

310
00:22:47,074 --> 00:22:48,494
- Dustin!
- Mike!

311
00:22:49,493 --> 00:22:50,373
Ada apa?

312
00:22:54,831 --> 00:22:56,501
Punya baterai lagi? AA?

313
00:22:56,583 --> 00:22:57,883
Untuk apa aku punya baterai?

314
00:22:57,959 --> 00:22:59,129
Aku selalu bawa baterai.

315
00:22:59,211 --> 00:23:00,461
Lalu apa masalahnya?

316
00:23:00,712 --> 00:23:02,632
- Aku butuh delapan.
- Delapan?

317
00:23:02,964 --> 00:23:05,634
Sial. Kita harus ke rencana B.

318
00:23:05,717 --> 00:23:07,547
Rencana B? Apa rencana B?

319
00:23:15,310 --> 00:23:17,100
Di mana mereka?

320
00:23:21,358 --> 00:23:22,478
Itu luar biasa.

321
00:23:22,943 --> 00:23:27,993
Di dalam aku tak begitu fokus,

322
00:23:28,073 --> 00:23:30,493
tapi kuyakin

323
00:23:31,451 --> 00:23:34,251
ibu itu ingin bercinta dengan putranya.

324
00:23:34,329 --> 00:23:36,869
Tunggu, wanita seksi itu
ibunya Alex P. Keaton?

325
00:23:36,957 --> 00:23:38,037
Ya, aku yakin.

326
00:23:38,125 --> 00:23:39,665
Usia mereka sama.

327
00:23:39,751 --> 00:23:41,751
Tapi Alex kembali ke masa lalu.

328
00:23:43,130 --> 00:23:44,970
Itu sebabnya disebut Back to the Future?

329
00:23:45,215 --> 00:23:47,675
Dia harus kembali ke masa depan

330
00:23:47,759 --> 00:23:49,679
karena dia di masa lalu.

331
00:23:49,761 --> 00:23:53,351
Jadi, masa depan adalah masa kini,
yaitu masanya.

332
00:23:57,477 --> 00:24:00,977
- Apa?
- Tidak, giliranku. Sudah cukup.

333
00:24:25,547 --> 00:24:26,757
Hei, Robin.

334
00:24:27,883 --> 00:24:29,553
Kau harus melihatnya.

335
00:24:31,428 --> 00:24:34,928
Lihat ini... Langit-langitnya indah.

336
00:25:20,685 --> 00:25:23,355
Tetap di sini,
jalankan rencana dengan Smirnoff.

337
00:25:23,438 --> 00:25:25,938
- Aku bisa bantu.
- Jangan, anak-anak akan takut.

338
00:25:26,024 --> 00:25:28,614
- Jim, jika ini soal tadi...
- Tetap di sini, Freud!

339
00:25:28,693 --> 00:25:30,703
Kau dengar? Tetap di sini.

340
00:25:36,576 --> 00:25:38,196
Terserah mau bilang apa soal Kline,

341
00:25:38,286 --> 00:25:40,406
tapi dia tahu benar cara mengadakan pesta.

342
00:25:40,830 --> 00:25:42,330
Omong-omong, aku kasihan padanya.

343
00:25:42,415 --> 00:25:43,915
- Siapa, Larry?
- Bukan, Murray.

344
00:25:44,000 --> 00:25:46,800
Dia orang gila yang suka
memengaruhi orang lain.

345
00:25:46,878 --> 00:25:50,088
Jadi, jangan sampai kita
terpengaruh olehnya.

346
00:25:50,173 --> 00:25:53,343
- Aku tidak, belum.
- Kau lebih diam dari biasanya.

347
00:25:53,426 --> 00:25:55,426
- Aku hanya ingin cari anak-anak.
- Ya.

348
00:25:55,512 --> 00:25:56,852
Kuusahakan semampuku.

349
00:26:00,267 --> 00:26:02,057
Terima kasih. Ini dia.

350
00:26:02,978 --> 00:26:03,978
Wali Kota Kline!

351
00:26:05,105 --> 00:26:06,145
Sekali lagi!

352
00:26:08,650 --> 00:26:11,110
Senyum yang lebar. Ini dia.

353
00:26:17,117 --> 00:26:19,157
- Awas!
- Selamat Hari Kemerdekaan, Berengsek.

354
00:26:26,001 --> 00:26:29,671
Angkatlah, Komunis Bajingan!

355
00:26:51,776 --> 00:26:53,486
- Diam.
- Maaf.

356
00:26:56,740 --> 00:26:59,950
- Bagaimana kau bisa meminumnya?
- Karena ini enak.

357
00:27:00,035 --> 00:27:01,035
Apa?

358
00:27:01,369 --> 00:27:03,119
Seperti The Thing-nya Carpenter.

359
00:27:03,204 --> 00:27:06,504
Yang asli adalah klasik,
tak perlu dipertanyakan lagi.

360
00:27:07,083 --> 00:27:08,383
Tapi pembuatan ulang itu...

361
00:27:18,720 --> 00:27:20,810
lebih manis, berani,

362
00:27:21,931 --> 00:27:22,771
lebih baik.

363
00:27:23,016 --> 00:27:24,136
Kau gila.

364
00:27:24,225 --> 00:27:26,805
Jadi, kau lebih suka Thing asli?

365
00:27:26,895 --> 00:27:30,145
Apa? Ini bukan soal The Thing,
tapi New Coke.

366
00:27:30,231 --> 00:27:31,651
Konsepnya sama.

367
00:27:31,733 --> 00:27:33,403
Sebenarnya tidak.

368
00:27:33,485 --> 00:27:34,605
Konsepnya sama.

369
00:27:34,694 --> 00:27:36,034
- Tidak sama.
- Sama.

370
00:27:36,279 --> 00:27:37,199
Hei.

371
00:27:38,114 --> 00:27:40,084
- Maaf.
- Maaf.

372
00:27:42,744 --> 00:27:44,584
Kau menemukannya?

373
00:27:47,916 --> 00:27:49,126
Bioskop?

374
00:27:49,209 --> 00:27:52,749
Dustin takut dengan gerbangnya,
sampai harus menonton film?

375
00:27:52,837 --> 00:27:54,047
Itu masuk akal.

376
00:27:54,130 --> 00:27:56,130
Kau yakin dia bilang "gerbang"
bukan "hebat"?

377
00:27:56,216 --> 00:27:58,046
Ya, seperti, "Film yang kutonton hebat."

378
00:27:58,134 --> 00:27:58,974
Mirip "gerbang".

379
00:27:59,052 --> 00:28:01,142
Yang menjadi alasan
Mind Flayer masih hidup.

380
00:28:01,221 --> 00:28:03,681
- Kita harus menutupnya lagi.
- Lalu monster itu mati.

381
00:28:03,765 --> 00:28:06,095
Tapi, jika tidak,
kita punya kembang api Lucas.

382
00:28:06,184 --> 00:28:08,774
Terus ejek rencanaku, Max.

383
00:28:08,853 --> 00:28:12,443
Aku ingin kau katakan lagi,
kau terus meragukanku.

384
00:28:12,524 --> 00:28:16,034
- Rencana konyol.
- Akan kubuktikan kau salah. Benar?

385
00:28:33,712 --> 00:28:35,882
Langit-langitku berhenti berputar.

386
00:28:36,464 --> 00:28:37,974
Kalau kau?

387
00:28:40,468 --> 00:28:41,638
Astaga.

388
00:28:42,595 --> 00:28:43,425
Tidak.

389
00:28:44,013 --> 00:28:45,853
Semuanya sudah kita muntahkan?

390
00:28:45,932 --> 00:28:48,272
Mungkin. Tanya sesuatu.

391
00:28:48,810 --> 00:28:50,060
Interogasi aku.

392
00:28:50,145 --> 00:28:51,935
Baik. Interogasi kau. Tentu.

393
00:28:53,648 --> 00:28:56,438
Kapan terakhir kau
buang air kecil di celana?

394
00:28:56,735 --> 00:28:57,685
Hari ini.

395
00:28:57,944 --> 00:28:58,784
Apa?

396
00:28:58,862 --> 00:29:00,782
Saat dokter Rusia
mengambil gergaji tulang.

397
00:29:01,030 --> 00:29:02,490
Astaga.

398
00:29:02,824 --> 00:29:04,494
Walau hanya sedikit.

399
00:29:04,576 --> 00:29:06,746
Ya, pasti masih ada di sistem kita.

400
00:29:10,290 --> 00:29:11,960
- Giliranku.
- Baik.

401
00:29:12,250 --> 00:29:13,170
Tanya aku.

402
00:29:14,294 --> 00:29:16,304
Kau pernah...

403
00:29:19,424 --> 00:29:20,764
jatuh cinta?

404
00:29:22,260 --> 00:29:25,600
Ya. Nancy Wheeler.
Semester pertama, tahun terakhir.

405
00:29:27,390 --> 00:29:28,810
Astaga.

406
00:29:29,601 --> 00:29:31,271
Dia centil.

407
00:29:33,855 --> 00:29:35,145
Ternyata, tidak juga.

408
00:29:36,775 --> 00:29:38,435
Apa kau masih mencintainya?

409
00:29:40,653 --> 00:29:42,033
- Tidak.
- Kenapa?

410
00:29:44,824 --> 00:29:47,494
Karena ada seseorang
yang lebih baik untukku.

411
00:29:48,620 --> 00:29:49,580
Ini gila.

412
00:29:50,497 --> 00:29:52,457
Sejak Dustin pulang, dia bilang,

413
00:29:52,540 --> 00:29:55,210
"Kau harus temukan Suzie-mu."

414
00:29:55,293 --> 00:29:56,633
Siapa Suzie?

415
00:29:56,711 --> 00:29:59,461
Gadis dari kamp, kurasa pacar Dustin.

416
00:29:59,714 --> 00:30:02,884
Sejujurnya, aku tak 100% yakin dia nyata.

417
00:30:04,511 --> 00:30:06,721
Tapi bukan itu intinya.

418
00:30:06,805 --> 00:30:09,765
Itu tak penting. Intinya,
gadis yang kusukai,

419
00:30:11,392 --> 00:30:15,062
adalah yang...
tak pernah kuajak bicara di sekolah.

420
00:30:16,606 --> 00:30:18,146
Aku tak tahu kenapa.

421
00:30:18,233 --> 00:30:21,113
Mungkin karena Tommy H.
akan mengolokku atau...

422
00:30:22,403 --> 00:30:25,703
aku tak akan jadi raja prom.

423
00:30:27,534 --> 00:30:31,044
Itu bodoh. Maksudku, Dustin benar,
itu hanya omong kosong.

424
00:30:31,120 --> 00:30:32,410
Karena, saat kupikirkan,

425
00:30:32,497 --> 00:30:34,787
seharusnya aku selalu bergaul dengannya.

426
00:30:34,874 --> 00:30:37,214
Pertama, dia lucu. Sangat lucu.

427
00:30:37,293 --> 00:30:40,173
Musim panas ini, aku lebih banyak tertawa

428
00:30:40,255 --> 00:30:43,675
daripada musim-musim sebelumnya.

429
00:30:43,925 --> 00:30:45,085
Dan dia cerdas.

430
00:30:46,427 --> 00:30:47,887
Lebih cerdas dariku.

431
00:30:49,305 --> 00:30:52,425
Dia bisa memecahkan
kode rahasia Rusia dan...

432
00:30:54,018 --> 00:30:57,148
Jujur, dia tak seperti
kebanyakan orang yang kutemui.

433
00:31:02,569 --> 00:31:03,399
Robin?

434
00:31:08,658 --> 00:31:10,288
Robin, kau overdosis?

435
00:31:11,160 --> 00:31:12,040
Tidak.

436
00:31:13,329 --> 00:31:16,459
Aku masih hidup.

437
00:31:26,843 --> 00:31:28,223
Lantainya menjijikkan.

438
00:31:28,720 --> 00:31:32,310
Ya, aku berdarah-darah
dan muntah di bajuku, jadi...

439
00:31:34,767 --> 00:31:35,847
Bagaimana menurutmu?

440
00:31:36,853 --> 00:31:37,813
Tentang?

441
00:31:38,313 --> 00:31:39,563
Gadis ini.

442
00:31:39,898 --> 00:31:40,938
Dia terdengar hebat.

443
00:31:41,190 --> 00:31:43,740
Dia memang hebat. Kalau prianya?

444
00:31:43,818 --> 00:31:46,988
Kurasa dia teler, dan tak berpikir jernih.

445
00:31:47,113 --> 00:31:49,783
Sungguh? Karena menurutku
pikirannya lebih jernih.

446
00:31:50,241 --> 00:31:51,411
Tidak.

447
00:31:53,328 --> 00:31:54,288
Dengar...

448
00:31:55,496 --> 00:31:58,116
dia bahkan tak kenal gadis ini.

449
00:31:58,625 --> 00:32:02,125
Dan jika kenal, benar-benar kenal,

450
00:32:02,921 --> 00:32:05,671
kurasa dia tak mau berteman.

451
00:32:05,882 --> 00:32:08,182
Tidak benar.

452
00:32:08,259 --> 00:32:09,839
Dengarkan aku, Steve.

453
00:32:10,303 --> 00:32:12,393
Itu mengejutkanku,

454
00:32:12,931 --> 00:32:14,391
tapi aku menyukaimu.

455
00:32:15,183 --> 00:32:16,683
Aku sangat menyukaimu.

456
00:32:17,393 --> 00:32:19,233
Tapi aku tak seperti temanmu yang lain.

457
00:32:19,979 --> 00:32:22,689
Dan aku tak seperti Nancy Wheeler.

458
00:32:22,982 --> 00:32:25,112
Itulah mengapa aku menyukaimu.

459
00:32:25,818 --> 00:32:28,448
Kau ingat perkataanku di kelas Bu Click?

460
00:32:28,696 --> 00:32:31,986
Soal aku cemburu dan terobsesi?

461
00:32:32,784 --> 00:32:33,664
Ya.

462
00:32:33,743 --> 00:32:37,003
Itu bukan karena aku suka padamu.

463
00:32:39,123 --> 00:32:40,213
Itu karena...

464
00:32:41,709 --> 00:32:43,879
dia tak berhenti menatapmu.

465
00:32:45,713 --> 00:32:46,713
Bu Click?

466
00:32:49,884 --> 00:32:51,434
Tammy Thompson.

467
00:32:53,137 --> 00:32:54,717
Aku ingin dia menatapku.

468
00:32:55,723 --> 00:32:59,023
Tapi dia tak bisa mengalihkan
pandangannya darimu

469
00:32:59,102 --> 00:33:02,192
dan rambut bodohmu.

470
00:33:03,231 --> 00:33:05,781
Aku tak mengerti, karena kau punya

471
00:33:06,651 --> 00:33:09,491
banyak remah bagel di lantai.

472
00:33:10,405 --> 00:33:15,195
Dan pertanyaanmu bodoh.
Dan kau berengsek.

473
00:33:15,702 --> 00:33:17,662
Dan kau bahkan tak suka dia dan...

474
00:33:17,996 --> 00:33:22,246
aku pulang dan berteriak di bantalku.

475
00:33:23,084 --> 00:33:25,344
Tapi Tammy Thompson seorang gadis.

476
00:33:27,046 --> 00:33:28,006
Steve.

477
00:33:28,673 --> 00:33:29,513
Ya?

478
00:33:38,307 --> 00:33:41,057
- Astaga.
- Benar.

479
00:33:42,145 --> 00:33:43,145
Astaga.

480
00:33:54,949 --> 00:33:56,029
